<Project>
  <PropertyGroup>
    <TargetFrameworks>net8.0;net10.0</TargetFrameworks>
    <LangVersion>preview</LangVersion>
    <Nullable>enable</Nullable>
    <ImplicitUsings>enable</ImplicitUsings>
    <InvariantGlobalization>false</InvariantGlobalization>
    <TreatWarningsAsErrors>true</TreatWarningsAsErrors>
    <Version>1.4.23</Version>
    <PackageReleaseNotes>
      A broad conformance release across pattern matching, modes/accumulators, XSLT 3.0 packages, xsl:copy namespaces, and XPath string literals. Patterns: chained predicates in a match pattern now use XPath filter semantics (each predicate re-indexes position()/last() against the survivors of the previous), and more pattern forms match (union/intersect operators, child::document-node(), a variable-reference pattern with a predicate, a parenthesized positional pattern, root() with a predicate). Modes: initial-mode="#default" selects the declared default mode; mode-scoped accumulators are evaluated on the streamed initial-mode path (with XTDE3362 for a non-applicable accumulator). Packages: xsl:original resolves for every overridden kind; accepted components are visible and validated; xsl:override static errors (XTSE0010/3050/3060) are diagnosed; component references and xsl:key/global/output/character-map/namespace-alias resolve package-locally; cross-package template import precedence (§6.6.2) and XTSE3050 conflicts are honoured; a used package's private components are no longer visible; @package-version selects the correct version. Serialization: xsl:copy-of copy-namespaces="no" no longer drops a copied element's own default namespace. Expressions: a raw &amp; in an XPath string literal parses. Requires PhoenixmlDb.Core 1.2.2 and PhoenixmlDb.XQuery 1.5.5. No breaking API changes. See RELEASES.md for full notes.
    </PackageReleaseNotes>
    <NoWarn>$(NoWarn);CS1591</NoWarn>
    <EnforceCodeStyleInBuild>true</EnforceCodeStyleInBuild>
    <AnalysisLevel>latest-all</AnalysisLevel>
  </PropertyGroup>

  <PropertyGroup>
    <Authors>Endpoint Systems</Authors>
    <Company>Endpoint Systems</Company>
    <Product>PhoenixmlDb</Product>
    <Copyright>Copyright © Endpoint Systems 2026. All rights reserved.</Copyright>
    <RepositoryType>git</RepositoryType>
    <RepositoryUrl>https://github.com/phoenixmldb/phoenixmldb-xslt</RepositoryUrl>
    <PackageProjectUrl>https://phoenixml.dev</PackageProjectUrl>
    <PackageLicenseExpression>Apache-2.0</PackageLicenseExpression>
    <PackageIcon>icon.png</PackageIcon>
    <PackageReadmeFile>PACKAGE.md</PackageReadmeFile>
    <GenerateDocumentationFile>true</GenerateDocumentationFile>
  </PropertyGroup>

  <ItemGroup>
    <None Include="$(MSBuildThisFileDirectory)icon.png" Pack="true" PackagePath="" />
    <None Include="$(MSBuildThisFileDirectory)PACKAGE.md" Pack="true" PackagePath="" />
  </ItemGroup>

  <PropertyGroup Condition="'$(Configuration)' == 'Release'">
    <DebugType>embedded</DebugType>
    <DebugSymbols>true</DebugSymbols>
    <Deterministic>true</Deterministic>
  </PropertyGroup>
</Project>
